# Retrieve pilot survey design
We retrieve details about the design of the pilot survey.

```{r }
dce_design_ls <- ingest(X,
                        fls_to_ingest_chr = ifelse(reproduce_1L_lgl,
                                                     "DDD_updated_dce_design_ls","CCC_updated_dce_design_ls"),
                        metadata_1L_lgl = F)
```
